history.text: Hello
I love the Toy Story series they are great.
still here
yes it is love the cast and seeing some of my favorite toys
which was your favorite installment in the series?
Probably the first one when the main character was a small boy and seen the world differently.

They are great I think they made a new one.
i heard that part 4 was in the making. wonder if they are going to continue with the little girl that has them now. cant wait to see what trouble they get into next. lol

This series could go forever like the Simpsons. Probably Woody he is real funny.

cartoon format fits well for this. i dont think it would work as well or translate as well as spongebob out of the water did.
Sure that is true. These cartoons give people imagination because the world is changing fast.

It just keeps getting better all the time.

yeah with each installment they went further and it worked well especially how woody and buzz relationship evolved
I think Andy is most right? I know he grown up later in the series.

yeah because i think growing up from kids to teenagers we may grow out of playing with ours toys but we always remember them and have a connection to them that takes us back to our childhood. definitely could relate to andy.
That is so true. Great movies and great life time memories.
so which villain did you like best. Lotso was hilarious

loved  how he looked so lovable but he was actually a mob leader of the toys. plus ned
